  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Addressing illegal deforestation through investigative journalism</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project is a collaboration between three partners (Mongabay, Earthsight and The Gecko Project) with the aim to document and publish news and media related to deforestation, corruption and forest crime. The project will focus on Brazil and Indonesia in addition to a global component. The project will use investigative journalism as a method, and publish a total of 10 larger featuring stories within 2020.</narrative>
  </description>
